  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908350/extras/631d3bca3169b73c5ced8574f0902c34.poster.avif?t=1752216708\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908350/extras/631d3bca3169b73c5ced8574f0902c34.webm?t=1752216708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908350/extras/631d3bca3169b73c5ced8574f0902c34.mp4?t=1752216708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>RUNR END is a challenging platformer set in a dreamish world.<br><br>Pull off cool movements while dodging traps and making precise jumps.<br>Discover secrets through your journey by paying attention to every detail the world has.<br>Oh, and I forgot to mention, there are <i>no checkpoints on levels</i>, who needs them anyway?<br><br><strong>Be careful,</strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908350/extras/5ac7b615bdf8ca71bd83614a59e22531.webp?t=1752216708\" width=600 height=52 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908350/extras/aa5ebee98a54ebd74472896041f0cfcc.poster.avif?t=1752216708\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908350/extras/aa5ebee98a54ebd74472896041f0cfcc.webm?t=1752216708\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1908350/extras/aa5ebee98a54ebd74472896041f0cfcc.mp4?t=1752216708\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A challenging campaign - No checkpoints on levels so you gotta be careful</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Make awesome movements</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Compete with your friends on Leaderboard</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Even compete with the DEV itself on Leaderboard :) </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Discover secrets and earn Achievements through your journey</li></ul>",
